      <title>2025 saw the end of the ‘I Inside the Old Year Dying’ tour in Australia and Japa...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DS7hTS6jJKD/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/608399130_18440027212106943_9161157819145245329_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc5OTc3NzE2NzE0ODg4Njk3Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=3nwF_Gv1tZsQ7kNvwH40Xxr&amp;_nc_oc=AdpKwNLW4ghxtU9XNhjWnkexiDOji9IlSTMgegChehdvF8yqWO5-qQslKY4-mQfV_q8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=tS-SxHlmrAtv60YeEqnk8A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxLZVdyR43TrrV9irrcr_EfEvpMZ1I5E9k96JZg96B_RQ&amp;oe=69C98970" alt="Instagram billede fra @pjharveyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@pjharveyofficial</strong></p><p>2025 saw the end of the ‘I Inside the Old Year Dying’ tour in Australia and Japan in March. The two-year tour was such a wonderful experience to have been a part of, and I hugely enjoyed being able bring the music to life in a shared experience.<br/>
<br/>
Since then I have been writing songs for my next album and poems for my next book, which is a process that always surprises and challenges me, but one I realise I am committed to and love.<br/>
<br/>
Here is a playlist of music I’ve been listening to this year and that I have found inspiring and strengthening.<br/>
<br/>
I wish you a happy and peaceful year ahead, and thank you for your support.<br/>
<br/>
Polly<br/>
<br/>
📸 @stevegullick, clothes @toddlynnlondon <br/>
<br/>
Link in profile.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/608399130_18440027212106943_9161157819145245329_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc5OTc3NzE2NzE0ODg4Njk3Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=3nwF_Gv1tZsQ7kNvwH40Xxr&amp;_nc_oc=AdpKwNLW4ghxtU9XNhjWnkexiDOji9IlSTMgegChehdvF8yqWO5-qQslKY4-mQfV_q8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=tS-SxHlmrAtv60YeEqnk8A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxLZVdyR43TrrV9irrcr_EfEvpMZ1I5E9k96JZg96B_RQ&amp;oe=69C98970" alt="Instagram billede fra @pjharveyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@pjharveyofficial</strong></p><p>2025 saw the end of the ‘I Inside the Old Year Dying’ tour in Australia and Japan in March. The two-year tour was such a wonderful experience to have been a part of, and I hugely enjoyed being able bring the music to life in a shared experience.<br/>
<br/>
Since then I have been writing songs for my next album and poems for my next book, which is a process that always surprises and challenges me, but one I realise I am committed to and love.<br/>
<br/>
Here is a playlist of music I’ve been listening to this year and that I have found inspiring and strengthening.<br/>
<br/>
I wish you a happy and peaceful year ahead, and thank you for your support.<br/>
<br/>
Polly<br/>
<br/>
📸 @stevegullick, clothes @toddlynnlondon <br/>
<br/>
Link in profile.</p>]]></content:encoded>
