      <title>PJ Harvey collaborator and friend @murphyseamus3 has released his latest book ‘S...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DOYCwyNjCyD/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/544113488_18421603861106943_272340255600313209_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNzY5NTM2OTY5MTA0NzgzMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-1jNet6rfXwQ7kNvwGvzrxx&amp;_nc_oc=Ado_sIrM_nSyGmyHDkVhmyv4yCer8YQd1pDcUr_Gu_RZ0K-C9fTQiBU8wzG--NVTPbI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=tS-SxHlmrAtv60YeEqnk8A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyGm3Rsqdp5sU1KB8menZIdJSU0VE0_oviL4iFZTr5gnQ&amp;oe=69C9B663" alt="Instagram billede fra @pjharveyofficial" /></p><p><strong>@pjharveyofficial</strong></p><p>PJ Harvey collaborator and friend @murphyseamus3 has released his latest book ‘Strange Love’ and appears on Tyler Cowen’s ‘Conversations with Tyler’ podcast. <br/>
<br/>
In this interview he talks about his journey as a photographer and filmmaker, and speaks about his work with PJ Harvey on both the ‘Let England Shake’ and ‘The Hope Six Demolition Project’ albums. <br/>
<br/>
‘Strange Love’ is out now.</p>]]></description>
